# 🏏 IPL Analytics & Match Prediction

A full end-to-end data science and machine learning pipeline analyzing Indian Premier League (IPL) cricket data from **Cricsheet (2008–2026)**. This project explores the deep statistical impact of the **Impact Player Rule**, builds robust player/venue insights, and deploys a live, client-side match outcome predictor.

